  <h1>About Bacoor City</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>City Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Bacoor City is a highly urbanized city located in the province of Cavite,
      Philippines. Known for its rich history and rapid development, Bacoor
      serves as a gateway between Metro Manila and Cavite.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Historical Background</h2>
    <p>
      Bacoor played a significant role in Philippine history, particularly during
      the Spanish colonial period and the Philippine Revolution. The city has
      since evolved into a major residential, commercial, and industrial hub.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Vision</h2>
    <p>
      A progressive, inclusive, and sustainable city committed to improving the
      quality of life of all Bacoore√±os through transparent governance and
      effective public service.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Mission</h2>
    <p>
      To deliver efficient and accessible government services, promote economic
      growth, uphold peace and order, and foster community participation in city
      development.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Core Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Integrity and Transparency</li>
      <li>Public Service Excellence</li>
      <li>Accountability</li>
      <li>Community Participation</li>
    </ul>
